{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":1,"timestamp":1770229876,"nonce":"n5ExHNFfb/GWbBZqj7RjKUse0PE=","metadata":{"github-id":"I_kwDOQ241x87oVNT8","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/164","origin":"github"},"title":"Create PR status dashboard script","message":"## Problem\n\nCurrently, identifying PRs that need attention requires manual scanning through PR lists to find:\n- PRs needing initial Copilot review\n- PRs with unresolved review comments (critical vs. minor)\n- PRs ready to merge\n\nThis is time-consuming and error-prone.\n\n## Proposed Solution\n\nCreate `.agent/scripts/pr_status.sh` that provides:\n\n1. **Basic Mode**: Status dashboard categorizing PRs by state\n   - 🟡 Needs Review (unreviewed commits)\n   - 🔴 Critical Issues (blocking comments)\n   - 🟠 Minor Issues (non-blocking comments)\n   - 🟢 Ready to Merge (approved, no issues)\n\n2. **Interactive Mode**: Menu-driven actions\n   - Launch Copilot review\n   - Hand off to agent for fixes\n   - Merge approved PRs\n   - Refresh status\n\n## Benefits\n\n- Reduces manual PR triage time\n- Clear visibility into PR pipeline status\n- Streamlines review → fix → merge workflow\n- Integrates with existing GitHub CLI tools\n\n## Implementation\n\n- Use `gh pr list`, `gh pr view`, GitHub API\n- Classify comments by severity\n- Track review status per commit\n- Provide actionable next steps\n\n---\n**🤖 Authored-By**: `Copilot CLI Agent`\n**🧠 Model**: `Claude Sonnet 4.5`","files":null}]}